description: The taoiseach (Irish prime minister) is also meeting Nancy Pelosi amid concerns over coronavirus.
title: St Patrick's Day: Leo Varadkar in US for Trump meeting
title_page: St Patrick's Day: Leo Varadkar in US for Trump meeting - BBC News
maintext: "I will use my meetings with President Trump and other senior US politicians to emphasise the strength and importance of Irish-US bilateral relations, particularly our economic ties," said Mr Varadkar.
